<div class="com-share" data-id="6284" data-title="《写字太累？这里有个机器人可以帮你手写》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6284/medium/6284.jpg?1436694588" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6284.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
